---
// Pediatric Healthy Start Service Page - Central Dentist (Detailed)
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Card from '../../components/ui/Card.astro';
import Button from '../../components/ui/Button.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Pediatric Healthy Start™ | Early Orthodontic Treatment | Central Dentist Dallas"
  description="Healthy Start™ System for early orthodontic intervention and airway development in children. Preventive pediatric dentistry at Central Dentist Dallas."
  schemaType="MedicalBusiness"
>
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-gradient-to-br from-olive to-lime-light text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto container-padding">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="font-heading text-h1 font-bold mb-6">
          Pediatric Healthy Start™ System
        </h1>
        <p class="font-body text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">
          Early intervention for optimal airway development and facial growth in children
        </p>
        <Button variant="secondary" size="lg" href="tel:214-368-0900">
          Schedule Child's Evaluation
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Is Healthy Start Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto container-padding">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-h2 font-semibold text-gray-dark mb-4">
            What is the Healthy Start™ System?
          </h2>
          <p class="font-body text-lg text-gray-medium">
            A comprehensive approach to early orthodontic intervention and airway development
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
          <div>
            <p class="font-body text-gray-medium mb-6 leading-relaxed">
              The Healthy Start™ System is an innovative approach to early orthodontic treatment that focuses 
              on the root causes of crooked teeth and poor jaw development. Rather than waiting until all 
              permanent teeth have erupted, this system addresses the underlying issues during the critical 
              developmental years between ages 2-15.
            </p>
            <p class="font-body text-gray-medium mb-6 leading-relaxed">
              This FDA-cleared system uses a series of soft, comfortable appliances that guide proper jaw 
              development, improve airway function, and create space for permanent teeth to erupt naturally 
              in their correct positions. The treatment is designed to work with your child's natural growth 
              patterns to achieve optimal results.
            </p>
            <p class="font-body text-gray-medium leading-relaxed">
              By addressing these issues early, we can often prevent the need for extensive orthodontic 
              treatment later, extractions, or jaw surgery, while also improving your child's breathing, 
              sleep quality, and overall development.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <Card variant="bordered" class="p-6">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-h4 font-semibold text-gray-dark mb-4">
              Key Features of Healthy Start™
            </h3>
            <ul class="font-body text-gray-medium space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-olive mr-2">✓</span>
                FDA-cleared treatment system
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-olive mr-2">✓</span>
                Soft, comfortable BPA-free appliances
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-olive mr-2">✓</span>
                Works during natural growth periods
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-olive mr-2">✓</span>
                Addresses root causes, not just symptoms
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-olive mr-2">✓</span>
                Improves airway and breathing function
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-olive mr-2">✓</span>
                Reduces need for future extractions
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-olive mr-2">✓</span>
                Enhances facial development
              </li>
            </ul>
          </Card>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Age Ranges and Treatment Phases -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-gray-light">
    <div class="container mx-auto container-padding">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-h2 font-semibold text-gray-dark mb-12 text-center">
          Treatment Phases by Age
        </h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <Card variant="hover" class="p-6 text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal to-teal-dark rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-heading text-2xl font-bold">
              2-5
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-h4 font-semibold text-gray-dark mb-4">
              Early Intervention
            </h3>
            <p class="font-body text-gray-medium mb-4 leading-relaxed">
              Focus on habit correction and establishing proper oral posture and breathing patterns.
            </p>
            <ul class="font-body text-gray-medium text-left space-y-2">
              <li>• Eliminate thumb sucking and pacifier habits</li>
              <li>• Encourage proper swallowing patterns</li>
              <li>• Promote nasal breathing</li>
              <li>• Improve tongue posture</li>
            </ul>
          </Card>
          
          <Card variant="hover" class="p-6 text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-olive to-lime-light rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-heading text-2xl font-bold">
              6-11
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-h4 font-semibold text-gray-dark mb-4">
              Growth Guidance
            </h3>
            <p class="font-body text-gray-medium mb-4 leading-relaxed">
              Guide proper jaw development and create space for permanent teeth.
            </p>
            <ul class="font-body text-gray-medium text-left space-y-2">
              <li>• Expand upper and lower arches</li>
              <li>• Guide jaw growth and positioning</li>
              <li>• Create space for permanent teeth</li>
              <li>• Improve airway development</li>
            </ul>
          </Card>
          
          <Card variant="hover" class="p-6 text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-lime-light to-teal rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-heading text-2xl font-bold">
              12-15
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-h4 font-semibold text-gray-dark mb-4">
              Final Alignment
            </h3>
            <p class="font-body text-gray-medium mb-4 leading-relaxed">
              Complete tooth alignment and finalize bite relationships.
            </p>
            <ul class="font-body text-gray-medium text-left space-y-2">
              <li>• Fine-tune tooth positioning</li>
              <li>• Establish proper bite relationships</li>
              <li>• Complete facial development</li>
              <li>• Optimize airway function</li>
            </ul>
          </Card>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Signs Your Child May Benefit -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto container-padding">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-h2 font-semibold text-gray-dark mb-8 text-center">
          Signs Your Child May Benefit from Healthy Start™
        </h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
          <Card variant="bordered" class="p-6">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-h4 font-semibold text-gray-dark mb-4">
              Sleep & Breathing Issues
            </h3>
            <ul class="font-body text-gray-medium space-y-2">
              <li>• Snoring or noisy breathing during sleep</li>
              <li>• Mouth breathing (especially at night)</li>
              <li>• Restless sleep or frequent waking</li>
              <li>• Bedwetting past age 5</li>
              <li>• Sleep apnea or breathing pauses</li>
              <li>• Grinding teeth at night (bruxism)</li>
            </ul>
          </Card>
          
          <Card variant="bordered" class="p-6">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-h4 font-semibold text-gray-dark mb-4">
              Facial & Dental Development
            </h3>
            <ul class="font-body text-gray-medium space-y-2">
              <li>• Crowded or crooked teeth</li>
              <li>• Protruding front teeth (overbite)</li>
              <li>• Underdeveloped lower jaw</li>
              <li>• Narrow upper or lower dental arches</li>
              <li>• Early or late loss of baby teeth</li>
              <li>• Difficulty chewing or swallowing</li>
            </ul>
          </Card>
          
          <Card variant="bordered" class="p-6">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-h4 font-semibold text-gray-dark mb-4">
              Behavioral & Development
            </h3>
            <ul class="font-body text-gray-medium space-y-2">
              <li>• ADHD-like symptoms or hyperactivity</li>
              <li>• Difficulty concentrating in school</li>
              <li>• Daytime fatigue or tiredness</li>
              <li>• Aggressive or irritable behavior</li>
              <li>• Poor academic performance</li>
              <li>• Speech difficulties or delays</li>
            </ul>
          </Card>
          
          <Card variant="bordered" class="p-6">
            <h3 class="font-heading text-h4 font-semibold text-gray-dark mb-4">
              Oral Habits & Posture
            </h3>
            <ul class="font-body text-gray-medium space-y-2">
              <li>• Thumb sucking past age 4</li>
              <li>• Extended pacifier use</li>
              <li>• Tongue thrusting or poor tongue posture</li>
              <li>• Lip sucking or biting habits</li>
              <li>• Forward head posture</li>
              <li>• Frequent open mouth posture</li>
            </ul>
          </Card>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Treatment Process -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-gray-light">
    <div class="container mx-auto container-padding">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-h2 font-semibold text-gray-dark mb-8 text-center">
          Our Healthy Start™ Treatment Process
        </h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <Card variant="hover" class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 mr-4 bg-teal rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-heading text-xl font-bold flex-shrink-0">
                1
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-h4 font-semibold text-gray-dark mb-2">
                  Comprehensive Evaluation
                </h3>
                <p class="font-body text-gray-medium">
                  Detailed assessment including 3D CBCT imaging, airway analysis, facial measurements, and 
                  development evaluation to determine if your child is a candidate for treatment.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </Card>
          
          <Card variant="hover" class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 mr-4 bg-olive rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-heading text-xl font-bold flex-shrink-0">
                2
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-h4 font-semibold text-gray-dark mb-2">
                  Custom Treatment Plan
                </h3>
                <p class="font-body text-gray-medium">
                  Development of a personalized treatment plan based on your child's specific needs, age, 
                  and developmental stage, with clear goals and timeline expectations.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </Card>
          
          <Card variant="hover" class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 mr-4 bg-lime-light rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-heading text-xl font-bold flex-shrink-0">
                3
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-h4 font-semibold text-gray-dark mb-2">
                  Appliance Fitting & Training
                </h3>
                <p class="font-body text-gray-medium">
                  Custom fitting of the Healthy Start™ appliance with comprehensive training for both 
                  child and parents on proper use, care, and what to expect during treatment.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </Card>
          
          <Card variant="hover" class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 mr-4 bg-teal-dark rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-heading text-xl font-bold flex-shrink-0">
                4
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-h4 font-semibold text-gray-dark mb-2">
                  Regular Monitoring & Adjustments
                </h3>
                <p class="font-body text-gray-medium">
                  Ongoing monitoring visits every 6-8 weeks to track progress, make necessary adjustments, 
                  and ensure optimal results throughout the treatment period.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </Card>
          
          <Card variant="hover" class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 mr-4 bg-olive rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-heading text-xl font-bold flex-shrink-0">
                5
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-h4 font-semibold text-gray-dark mb-2">
                  Completion & Retention
                </h3>
                <p class="font-body text-gray-medium">
                  Upon completion of active treatment, we provide retention protocols to maintain results 
                  and ensure long-term stability of the improvements achieved.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </Card>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Benefits Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto container-padding">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-h2 font-semibold text-gray-dark mb-8 text-center">
          Long-term Benefits for Your Child
        </h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-h4 font-semibold text-gray-dark mb-6">
              Immediate Improvements
            </h3>
            <ul class="font-body text-gray-medium space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-teal mr-2">✓</span>
                Better sleep quality and reduced snoring
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-teal mr-2">✓</span>
                Improved breathing and airway function
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-teal mr-2">✓</span>
                Enhanced concentration and school performance
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-teal mr-2">✓</span>
                Better behavior and emotional regulation
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-teal mr-2">✓</span>
                Reduced bedwetting and sleep disruptions
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-teal mr-2">✓</span>
                Improved speech and swallowing patterns
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-h4 font-semibold text-gray-dark mb-6">
              Long-term Advantages
            </h3>
            <ul class="font-body text-gray-medium space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-olive mr-2">✓</span>
                Reduced need for tooth extractions
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-olive mr-2">✓</span>
                Shorter traditional orthodontic treatment
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-olive mr-2">✓</span>
                Improved facial development and profile
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-olive mr-2">✓</span>
                Better overall health and wellness
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-olive mr-2">✓</span>
                Reduced risk of TMJ disorders
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-olive mr-2">✓</span>
                Enhanced self-confidence and self-esteem
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Parent Testimonials Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-gray-light">
    <div class="container mx-auto container-padding">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-h2 font-semibold text-gray-dark mb-8 text-center">
          What Parents Are Saying
        </h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <Card variant="bordered" class="p-6">
            <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
              {Array.from({ length: 5 }, (_, i) => (
                <svg key={i} class="w-5 h-5 text-lime-light" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path>
                </svg>
              ))}
            </div>
            <blockquote class="font-body text-gray-dark leading-relaxed mb-4 italic text-center">
              "My 8-year-old son was having trouble sleeping and concentrating in school. After just 6 months 
              with Healthy Start™, his sleep improved dramatically, and his teachers noticed a big difference 
              in his focus and behavior."
            </blockquote>
            <cite class="font-body text-gray-medium font-semibold text-center block">
              — Sarah M., Dallas Parent
            </cite>
          </Card>
          
          <Card variant="bordered" class="p-6">
            <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
              {Array.from({ length: 5 }, (_, i) => (
                <svg key={i} class="w-5 h-5 text-lime-light" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path>
                </svg>
              ))}
            </div>
            <blockquote class="font-body text-gray-dark leading-relaxed mb-4 italic text-center">
              "We avoided extractions and years of traditional braces! My daughter's teeth came in beautifully 
              straight, and her breathing has improved so much. The investment in Healthy Start™ was absolutely 
              worth it."
            </blockquote>
            <cite class="font-body text-gray-medium font-semibold text-center block">
              — Jennifer L., Plano Parent
            </cite>
          </Card>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-gradient-to-br from-olive to-lime-light text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto container-padding text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-h2 font-bold mb-6">
        Give Your Child the Healthy Start™ They Deserve
      </h2>
      <p class="font-body text-lg mb-8 opacity-90 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Early intervention can prevent years of complex treatment and give your child a lifetime of better 
        breathing, sleeping, and overall health. Schedule a consultation to see if Healthy Start™ is right 
        for your child.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mb-6">
        <Button variant="secondary" size="lg" href="tel:214-368-0900">
          Call (214) 368-0900
        </Button>
        <Button variant="outline" size="lg" href="/contact">
          Schedule Consultation
        </Button>
      </div>
      <p class="font-body text-sm opacity-75">
        The earlier we start, the better the results. Don't wait - your child's development window is limited.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>